title: Football Manager 2008 8.0.2 Mac nocd crack
description:
This is a crack for the MAC-version of Football Manager 2008 v8.0.2.
Apart from all other cracks around, this one works :)

Instructions:

- Install Fm2008 on your mac and update it to 8.0.2.
- Replace the old fm.exe from your gamedir, with the one in the zip-file.

Btw...I think you need to have the game-image mounted with toast or any other program for it to work. Not sure though.
